{
  "texts": [
    "In some datasets, the T5-based method has achieved good results.",
    "Overall, this method has advantages in performance and flexibility, but the impact of factors such as training datasets and model parameters must be considered.",
    "However, compared with the methods based on the T5 model, ChatGPT has some limitations or challenges in the ACOSQE task.",
    "Firstly, ChatGPT requires complex prompts to define the structure and format of the quadruples, which may affect the user experience and model efficiency.",
    "Secondly, ChatGPT's performance is unstable when dealing with a long tail and complex scenarios, and there is a significant performance gap compared with specially designed models."
  ]
}